name: Opium Days / The Earworm pt.1
description: Lore Token #1 from the Limbo Universe Collection. This illustration is a remastered version of the very first illustration Limbo ever created taking place in his specific universe. The vision of a gigantic ear appearing in the sky as a vessel between realms of consciousness has a very profound esoteric meaning. This token is a rare special edition airdropped to LU collectors for Christmas 2021.
